title: Clinton vows to make gun safety a central theme of her campaign
text: KEENE, N.H. — Hillary Rodham Clinton vowed to make gun safety a central theme of her presidential campaign, saying here Friday that too many people in public life are "intimidated" by talking about gun control and promising that she would do so loudly.
